    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔发表经济评论后，美国国债收益率回落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/treasury-market-closes-in-on-historic-five-month-winning-streak</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示美国经济依然稳固，令美国国债市场连续第五个月的历史性涨幅缩水，债券交易员降低了对未来一年降息的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/treasury-market-closes-in-on-historic-five-month-winning-streak</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 16:23:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
